  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Scout-Nin Keyword: Specialized </p><p>When you cast a Combo and Finisher during your turn, you can spend 1 superiority die to immediately impose a Dexterity saving throw against one affected creature, with a penalty to their saving throw equal to half the result of the superiority die.</p><p> On a failed save, you slash at the creature's eyes, dealing your weapon's damage and blinding them until the end of your next turn.</p><p> A large or bigger creature makes this save at disadvantage.</p><p></p>",
